1
00:00:05,209 --> 00:00:06,718
Murakaza neza nanone

2
00:00:06,719 --> 00:00:12,241
Aka ni  agace ka 5.2 <i>Gufata agaciro</i>.

3
00:00:12,242 --> 00:00:14,384
Kugeza ubu ni iki mwakoze kuri iri somo?

4
00:00:14,385 --> 00:00:18,600
twavuze byinshi
kubijyanye no kurinda imitungo n'ibihangano

5
00:00:18,601 --> 00:00:20,982
Noneho aha ho tugiye gufata
indi ntabwe yisumbuyeho.

6
00:00:20,983 --> 00:00:26,283
ubundi tuvuge kuburyo ibigo
bishobora kugira amafaranga mu bihangano byabo.

7
00:00:27,203 --> 00:00:28,904
Reka dutangire n'ubusobanuro bumwe na bumwe.

8
00:00:28,905 --> 00:00:31,593
Mbere na mbere, udushya ni iki?

9
00:00:32,491 --> 00:00:35,956
Udushya ni ugukoresha ubwenge bushya

10
00:00:35,957 --> 00:00:40,262
mu kuzana ibicuruzwa bishya,
serivisi, cyangwa uburyo bushyashya.

11
00:00:41,149 --> 00:00:47,634
Kandi biba birimo ibihangano,
ibijyanye n'ibicuruzwa, ndetse na n'ibintu biboneye.

12
00:00:47,964 --> 00:00:49,400
Reka tuvuge kuri ibyo.

13
00:00:49,401 --> 00:00:51,221
Murebye kuri iki gishushanyo:

14
00:00:51,222 --> 00:00:56,781
Igihangano gitekerezwa nko kuba
ubushakashatsi n'iterambere,

15
00:00:56,782 --> 00:01:01,349
igitekerezo cyibanze cya mbere
ku gicuruzwa, uburyo, cyangwa serivisi nshyashya.

16
00:01:02,256 --> 00:01:07,533
Icuruza ni iterambere ry'igicuruzwa
no kuzana igicuruzwa ku isoko.

17
00:01:08,459 --> 00:01:13,709
Noneho, bwa nyuma, ibiboneye,
cyangwa <i> kunoza </i>,

18
00:01:13,734 --> 00:01:19,994
ijyanye no kubona amafaranga ndetse no gufata agaciro
bivuye mu bihangano ku isoko.

19
00:01:19,995 --> 00:01:24,652
Tugiye kwibanda cyane
ku iboneza muri iki gice.

20
00:01:25,508 --> 00:01:30,416
Iboneza, cyangwa inozwa
ni ribabanda cyane

21
00:01:30,417 --> 00:01:33,335
ku gitekerezo cyo <i> kwigana </i> .

22
00:01:34,062 --> 00:01:38,579
Kwigana ni ubushobozi bw'undi muntu

23
00:01:38,580 --> 00:01:42,820
bwo kwigana igihangano cy'umushoramari.

24
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:47,568
Kandi kigendana n'iboneza
muri ubu buryo:

25
00:01:47,569 --> 00:01:53,442
iyo byoroshye kwigana ikintu,
ubwo ukukigana kuba kuri hejuru;

26
00:01:53,443 --> 00:01:56,344
biba bigoye cyane kuri nyir' igihangano

27
00:01:56,345 --> 00:01:58,845
kubona amafaranga muri rusange
kubona agaciro.

28
00:02:00,513 --> 00:02:04,942
Kandi iyo bigoye kwigana ikintu
ibyo bisobanura ko kucyigana ari guke.

29
00:02:05,842 --> 00:02:08,972
Nyuma ibyo ni byo byoroshye ku mushoramari

30
00:02:08,973 --> 00:02:12,086
mu kubona agaciro
gaturutse mu bihangano bye.

31
00:02:12,087 --> 00:02:16,389
Abantu benshi batekereza 
ko kwigana ari ibintu byibanze

32
00:02:16,390 --> 00:02:19,308
bijyanye no kurinda imitungo n'ibihangano.

33
00:02:19,309 --> 00:02:20,789
Kandi ibyo bishobora kuba ukuri.

34
00:02:20,790 --> 00:02:24,519
Ariko, ari ingero nyinshi
aho kurinda imitungo n'ibihangano

35
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:28,244
atari ikintu cy'ibanze mu kwigana.

36
00:02:28,245 --> 00:02:32,500
Nk'urugero, byagorana kwigana ikihangano

37
00:02:32,501 --> 00:02:37,584
nubwo haba hari irindwa rike cyangwa ntaryo
kuri icyo gicuruzwa cyangwa serivisi.

38
00:02:37,607 --> 00:02:41,061
Ibyo byakorwa
mu buryo butandukanye

39
00:02:41,062 --> 00:02:44,449
Harimo ikomezwa; aho bitumvikana

40
00:02:44,450 --> 00:02:48,640
uburyo ibicuruzwa bishyirwa hamwe

41
00:02:48,641 --> 00:02:51,930
cyangwa ibiba ku gicuruzwa.

42
00:02:51,931 --> 00:02:54,640
Bishobora kuba mu bumenyi bwumvikana,

43
00:02:54,641 --> 00:02:58,242
aho umushoramari
aba afite ubumenyi bw'umwihariko

44
00:02:58,243 --> 00:03:03,523
bugoye gutondekanya no gutangaza
kandi bushobora kwigwa mu kazi.

45
00:03:04,534 --> 00:03:06,733
Ibyo nabyo byagorana kubyigana.

46
00:03:06,734 --> 00:03:10,784
Noneho bwa nyuma, iyo hari byinshi
biri mu nzira z'udushya

47
00:03:10,785 --> 00:03:14,459
Inyuma y'isohorwa
ry'igicuruzwa cyangwa serivisi.

48
00:03:15,340 --> 00:03:19,690
Inzira z'udushya akenshi
ziba zigoye kuzibona

49
00:03:19,691 --> 00:03:23,080
Kandi, bigoye
kwigana igicuruzwa cya nyuma.

50
00:03:23,967 --> 00:03:26,109
Reka tuvuge ku
<i>mitungo itaramba</i>.

51
00:03:27,724 --> 00:03:31,175
Ikintu cya mbere dushaka kumenya ni:
umutungo utaramba ni iki?

52
00:03:31,741 --> 00:03:35,676
Umutungo utaramba ni buri kintu

53
00:03:35,677 --> 00:03:38,676
gikenerwa mu igurishwa ry'igihangano

54
00:03:38,677 --> 00:03:41,912
bitandukanye na tekinologi ubwayo.

55
00:03:41,913 --> 00:03:44,879
Noneho ni izihe ngero
z'imitungo itimukanwa?

56
00:03:45,987 --> 00:03:49,654
Watekereza ibicuruzwa
n'ikwirakwiza,

57
00:03:50,892 --> 00:03:54,898
itunganywa ry'igicuruzwa cyawe,
imenyekanishwa ry'igicuruzwa,

58
00:03:55,758 --> 00:03:59,537
ndetse n'ikindi kintu cyose wakora
mu kuzana igucuruzwa cyawe ku isoko

59
00:03:59,538 --> 00:04:04,172
hirya yo guteza imbere
umushinga cyangwa ikoranabuhanga ubwaryo.

60
00:04:04,173 --> 00:04:06,288
Tekereza ko uri umwe
mu ruhererekane rw'itanga.

61
00:04:06,981 --> 00:04:10,010
Ushobora gutumiza ibikoresho by'ibanze
biturutse ku mu fatanyabikorwa.

62
00:04:10,011 --> 00:04:13,143
Ushobora gukora gahunda zimwe
kuri icyo kugirango ubone igicuruzwa.

63
00:04:13,144 --> 00:04:16,195
Ukeneye umuntu wo kugenda
akagucururiza igicuruzwa.

64
00:04:16,196 --> 00:04:22,047
Kandi ushobora no gushaka gukwirakwiza
icyo gicuruzwa ku bantu ngo bakigure.

65
00:04:22,961 --> 00:04:26,098
Izo ngingo zose,
ziri ku ruhande rw'igicuruzwa ubwacyo,

66
00:04:26,099 --> 00:04:29,869
ushobora gushaka uburenganzira
ku bikoresho byuzuzanya.

67
00:04:31,248 --> 00:04:35,805
Noneho, ikibazo ni:
Ese ni kimwe n'igicuruzwa cyuzuzanya?

68
00:04:35,806 --> 00:04:38,749
Kandi igisubizo ni: oya, iki ntabwo ari
kimwe n'igicuruzwa cyuzuzanya.


69
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:42,382
Igicuruzwa cyuzuzanya kimeze nk'inkweto
na rase z'inkweto, urabizi.

70
00:04:42,383 --> 00:04:47,298
Iyo igiciro cy'inkweto cyiyongereye,
igiciro cy'amarasi cyiragabanuka.

71
00:04:47,299 --> 00:04:50,280
Ibyo bicuruzwa bibiri
bikoreshwa icyarimwe

72
00:04:50,281 --> 00:04:52,221
kandi biruzuzanya.

73
00:04:52,222 --> 00:04:53,603
Bityo, icyo ni igicuruzwa cyunganirana.

74
00:04:53,604 --> 00:04:56,138
Icyo turi kuvugaho hano
ni ibikoresho byunganirana,

75
00:04:56,139 --> 00:05:00,121
ari bwo bushobozi
kuri bimwe bikenewe

76
00:05:00,122 --> 00:05:03,121
mu kugurisha ibihangano byawe.

77
00:05:03,122 --> 00:05:04,709
Ikibazo kenshi kiba:

78
00:05:05,442 --> 00:05:09,600
ni ryari nkeneye gutekereza
ku mitungo yuzuzanya?

79
00:05:09,601 --> 00:05:12,059
Kandi uburyo
bwo tukunda gutekerezamo bino

80
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:17,156
ni ugufata umutungo wuzuzanya
umwe mu gihe kimwe tukagisuzuma tukavuga,

81
00:05:17,157 --> 00:05:18,786
"Ese birakwiye kuri njye?"

82
00:05:18,787 --> 00:05:21,240
"Ese mfite kwita kuri kino
kintu by'umwihariko?"

83
00:05:22,309 --> 00:05:25,231
Kandi kuri ibyo, tugiye gukuza
ikintu cy'umurimo gato

84
00:05:25,232 --> 00:05:29,957
ku gutekereza niba ukwiye kwita
kuri buri mutungo wuzuzanya.

85
00:05:29,958 --> 00:05:35,062
Ndi gutanga igitekerezo ko uburyo bwo gutekereza ku
mutungo wuzuzanya

86
00:05:35,063 --> 00:05:40,505
buboneye kuri mwe ari ugutekereza ku
ngero ebyeri zitandukanye.

87
00:05:40,506 --> 00:05:44,457
Icyambere ni: ni umutungo
ifite akamaro cyangwa ntako?

88
00:05:46,138 --> 00:05:50,818
Icyakabiri ni: niba ari icy'agaciro,
ninde ungenga umutungo?

89
00:05:51,645 --> 00:05:55,904
Ese byaba biri mu irushanwa mw'itanga,
mu yandi magambo biboneka byososhye?

90
00:05:55,905 --> 00:06:00,423
Cyangwa byaba bigumanwa
na rimwe cyangwa amatsinda abiri?

91
00:06:01,728 --> 00:06:06,001
Noneho iyo urebye kuri iki gishushanyo,
icyo ubona ni ibintu bine

92
00:06:06,002 --> 00:06:08,960
zibanze ku mbumbe
z'ibi bintu.

93
00:06:08,961 --> 00:06:11,505
Noneho tuvuge nk'uruhande ruto rw'iburyo,

94
00:06:11,506 --> 00:06:14,092
ni uko ufite
umutungo wuzuzanya w'ingirakamaro,

95
00:06:14,093 --> 00:06:17,956
ariko umutungo wuzuzanya ubwawo
ku bwingenge bwawo uba uhari.

96
00:06:17,957 --> 00:06:21,193
Reka tuvuge ko wakoze isaha isanzwe.

97
00:06:21,194 --> 00:06:24,808
Ntabwo ari nziza kandi yubakiye
ku bikoresho by'ubuziranenge

98
00:06:24,809 --> 00:06:26,453
wanabona no kuyandi masaha.

99
00:06:26,454 --> 00:06:30,704
Noneho ushobora kwibaza
niba ushobora kwita

100
00:06:30,705 --> 00:06:33,376
ku ifungwa ry'iyo saha.

101
00:06:33,377 --> 00:06:37,794
Ese ifungwa ni umutungo wuzazanya
w'akamaro?

102
00:06:38,744 --> 00:06:41,084
kandi nkeka ko igisubizo ari yego.

103
00:06:41,085 --> 00:06:45,471
Ukeneye kugera ku bagufasha gufunga
kugirango ubashe kugurisha isaha yawe.

104
00:06:46,567 --> 00:06:51,256
Ariko, Nanatanga igitekerezo
ko iboneka ku buntu.

105
00:06:51,257 --> 00:06:55,181
Hari abantu bagufasha gufunga hanze aha
bakwifuza kugira businesi yawe.

106
00:06:55,182 --> 00:06:56,800
Nanone ndatekereza hamwe no kwitaba amatelephoni amwe

107
00:06:56,801 --> 00:07:00,588
washobora kuba wamaze kubona abakwemerera benshi
wicaye aho mu masaha make.

108
00:07:00,589 --> 00:07:04,294
Noneho kubwibyo, turabona ko ibi bigiye
kuba mu ruhande ruto rw'uburyo

109
00:07:04,295 --> 00:07:09,524
aho umutungo wuzuzanya uba ari ingenzi
ariko uri mu irushanwa ry'itanga,

110
00:07:09,525 --> 00:07:11,341
cyangwa uhari byoroshye.

111
00:07:11,342 --> 00:07:17,298
Noneho tekereza aho kugira isaha isanzwe
ko wahanze nka porogaramu ya software.

112
00:07:18,930 --> 00:07:24,332
Wakwibaza niba ugufunga
ariwo mutungo wuzuzanya

113
00:07:24,333 --> 00:07:26,798
kuri icyo gicuruzwa cya software cyawe.

114
00:07:27,707 --> 00:07:31,676
Ariko aha ndakeka abantu benshi bavuga
ko uburyo bwo gufunga

115
00:07:31,677 --> 00:07:37,114
birashoboka ko atari ingenzi cyane
kuri porogaramu ya software.

116
00:07:37,115 --> 00:07:40,193
Noneho twibona hano
ku ruhande rwo kuruhande rw'imoso

117
00:07:40,194 --> 00:07:43,209
ariwo mutungo wuzuzanya ubwawo

118
00:07:43,210 --> 00:07:46,696
iba idafite akamaro nubwo yaba
ari ubuntu ku isoko.

119
00:07:46,697 --> 00:07:49,444
Noneho reka turebe urugero rutandukanye

120
00:07:49,445 --> 00:07:53,590
aho wakoze
porogaramu ya software muri telephoni.

121
00:07:55,146 --> 00:07:57,262
Noneho ukaba wibaza

122
00:07:57,263 --> 00:08:01,672
nubwo wakwita
kuri App Store,

123
00:08:01,673 --> 00:08:04,879
ni abahe bantu bo kugeraho
kuri porogaramu yawe.

124
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:07,342
Ndakeka aha twakwemera

125
00:08:07,343 --> 00:08:11,633
aho bacururiza porogaramu, cyangwa andi maduka nkayo
nka Google Play Store,

126
00:08:11,634 --> 00:08:15,290
byaba bikwiye cyane
ku ikwirakwiza rya porogaramu yawe.

127
00:08:16,282 --> 00:08:18,146
Kandi noneho,
no gucuruza igicuruzwa cyawe,

128
00:08:18,147 --> 00:08:21,322
ugiye gushaka ubwende
kuri iyo App Store.

129
00:08:22,656 --> 00:08:29,564
Ariko ikibabaje kuri wowe, ni uko App Store
ifitwe kandi igacugwa n'umushinga umwe.

130
00:08:29,565 --> 00:08:31,887
Kandi niba uri gutekereza ku yandi matelefoni,

131
00:08:31,888 --> 00:08:35,813
Muri rusange, ikwirakwiza
kuri izo telefoni rigizwe

132
00:08:35,813 --> 00:08:38,054
n'umubare muto w'imishinga.

133
00:08:38,054 --> 00:08:41,097
Noneho aho niho twisanga
mu ruhande rwo hejuru rw'iburyo

134
00:08:41,099 --> 00:08:45,758
ariho umutungo wuzuzanya
uba ingenzi kandi ukagirwa.

135
00:08:45,759 --> 00:08:50,873
Kandi ibyo bisobanuy ko nyiri App Store,
muri uru rugero rw'umwihariko Apple,

136
00:08:50,874 --> 00:08:54,044
izaba icunga byinshi
byo kuganiraho

137
00:08:54,045 --> 00:09:00,003
no gucunga amategeko y'ibyemeranijwe
by'amasezerano yo gusangira umutungo.

138
00:09:01,355 --> 00:09:05,791
Ikiyongereyeho, umucunga
w'umutungo wuzuzanya ashobora kwanzura

139
00:09:05,792 --> 00:09:09,473
Niba akwemera cyangwa aguhakana
muri App Store.

140
00:09:09,474 --> 00:09:14,489
Noneho bwa nyuma, reka tuvuge ko wazanye
mu kimbo cya porogaramu ya telefoni,

141
00:09:14,490 --> 00:09:20,784
wazanye ububiko bushya 
bwa telefoni, cyangwa ikintu nk'icyo.

142
00:09:20,785 --> 00:09:25,447
Noneho, kino kibazo cy'umwihariko
cyakorwa n'igikoresho gishya

143
00:09:25,448 --> 00:09:28,178
cyangwa bifite ibindi bikoresho
bishakwa.

144
00:09:29,503 --> 00:09:32,266
Noneho aho reka turebe
ku kibazo cya telefoni,

145
00:09:32,267 --> 00:09:37,967
kandi reka turebe no kuri App Store
nk'uruhererekane mw'itanga.

146
00:09:37,968 --> 00:09:41,114
Noneho, kuri iki kibazo cy'umwihariko, ndakeka
ko abantu benshi bakwemera

147
00:09:41,115 --> 00:09:46,141
ko App Store atari mu by'ukuri
iy'ingenzi mu ruhererekane rw'itanga.

148
00:09:46,142 --> 00:09:49,188
Nubwo ifitwe by'umwihariko na Apple,

149
00:09:49,189 --> 00:09:52,856
ntabwo iri buhungabanye
ikibazo kiri mu itangwa ry' ububiko bwa telefoni.

150
00:09:52,857 --> 00:09:55,259
Ibyo byaba bihabanye rwose
mu ruhererekane rw'itanga.

151
00:09:55,260 --> 00:10:00,030
Kandi ubwo App Store aha ntabwo ari iy'ingenzi
kuri wowe nk'umushoramari.

152
00:10:00,031 --> 00:10:04,131
Noneho nk'uko ushobora kubibona, hari
gusa ubwo bubiri bw'umusaruro aha.

153
00:10:04,132 --> 00:10:09,006
Kandi umwe wonyine
wo abashoramari bibandaho.

154
00:10:09,007 --> 00:10:13,515
Nagabanyijemo ibyo mo amabara abiri:
zoni y'umutuku na zoni y'icyatsi.

155
00:10:13,516 --> 00:10:18,080
Zoni y'umutuku ni ikibazo
aho umutungo wuzuzanya

156
00:10:18,081 --> 00:10:22,715
uba ufitwe kandi ari uw'ingenzi
ku mushoramari.

157
00:10:22,716 --> 00:10:25,578
Noneho izindi ngingo eshatu,
tuzishyira muri zoni y'icyatsi

158
00:10:25,579 --> 00:10:28,177
Kubera ko ibyo atari
ikibazo cyane ku mushoramari.

159
00:10:28,178 --> 00:10:34,146
Hamwe umutungo wuzuzanya
ntabwo uri ingenzi, aho twamaze kuhabona,

160
00:10:34,147 --> 00:10:36,095
cyangwa ukaba ubonekera ubuntu,

161
00:10:36,096 --> 00:10:39,295
Ni mu ruhe rwego ari itanga ry'ipiganwa
kandi dushobora no kubiganiraho

162
00:10:39,296 --> 00:10:42,295
hamwe n'abagemura benshi
ngo baduhe ibyiza.

163
00:10:42,296 --> 00:10:46,139
Noneho turi kugerageza gufata agaciro
ku bihangano byacu.

164
00:10:46,140 --> 00:10:48,157
Tugiye ku kindi gishushanyo,

165
00:10:48,158 --> 00:10:53,121
icyo nakoze ni uko nafashe zoni y'umutuku
nkayishyira ku ruhande rw'iburyo.

166
00:10:53,122 --> 00:10:56,619
Iyo ni yo zoni
aho umutungo wuzuzanya

167
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:59,817
iba ari iyingenzi kdi ikomejwe cyane.

168
00:10:59,818 --> 00:11:03,523
Kandi ku ruhande rw'ibumoso
kuri iyi mbonerahamwe hari zoni y'icyatsi.

169
00:11:04,583 --> 00:11:08,613
Muri zoni y'icyatsi niho haba
atari ah'ingenzi cyangwa habonekera ubuntu.

170
00:11:09,627 --> 00:11:11,956
Ibyo biraringaniye mu maso
ya rwiyemezamirimo.

171
00:11:11,957 --> 00:11:14,483
Kandi noneho, ku ruhande rw'ubumuso,

172
00:11:14,484 --> 00:11:19,457
icyo dufite nuko dusubira inyuma
ku meza yo kwiganana,

173
00:11:19,458 --> 00:11:23,627
noneho dushobora gutandukanya
hagati y'ibintu bigoye kwigana,

174
00:11:23,628 --> 00:11:25,733
icyo ni <i> ukwiganana gucye </i>,

175
00:11:25,734 --> 00:11:30,250
cyangwa ibintu byoroshye
kubyigana, ibyo ni <i>ukwiganana kwinshi</i>.

176
00:11:30,251 --> 00:11:33,843
Noneho aha icyo tugiye 
kureba ni

177
00:11:33,844 --> 00:11:39,054
ninde ufata agaciro kavuye mu bihangano
muri buri gice cya kino gishushanyo?

178
00:11:39,055 --> 00:11:40,600
Kandi ntabwo ari bimwe.

179
00:11:41,933 --> 00:11:44,697
Reka turebe ku ruhande rw'ubumoso.

180
00:11:44,698 --> 00:11:51,208
Uruhande rwo hejuru rw'ubumoso aha ni ikibazo
aho imitungo yuzuzanya

181
00:11:51,209 --> 00:11:56,251
bidakenewe cyangwa se bibonekera ubuntu,
kandi kubyigana bigoye.

182
00:11:56,277 --> 00:11:58,227
Noneho aha hari ikibazo aho umushoramari

183
00:11:58,228 --> 00:12:00,533
aba afite igicuruzwa cyangwa serivisi
ibyo biragoye kubyigana,

184
00:12:00,534 --> 00:12:05,345
kandi imitungo yose yuzuzanya
iba ibonekera ubuntu

185
00:12:05,346 --> 00:12:06,971
cyangwa ari iy'ingenzi.

186
00:12:06,972 --> 00:12:08,834
iyo bigenze gutya

187
00:12:08,835 --> 00:12:14,188
umushoramari cyangwa nyir'ingihangano aba agiye
gufata agaciro kuri icyo gihangano.

188
00:12:15,765 --> 00:12:18,482
ikindi gitandukanye nicyo ni
igice cyo hasi cy'iburyo.

189
00:12:18,483 --> 00:12:22,265
Icyo ni igihe
aho umutungo yuzuzanya

190
00:12:22,266 --> 00:12:29,679
uba ari ingenzi kandi ufitwe
n'umushoramari,

191
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:32,951
biba byoroshye kwigana icyo gicuruzwa cyangwa serivisi.

192
00:12:32,952 --> 00:12:36,674
Nanone, hari nkuko mubibona,
nyir'umutungo wuzuzanya

193
00:12:36,675 --> 00:12:39,960
agiye kuba mu mwanya ukomeye
wo guciririkanya.

194
00:12:39,961 --> 00:12:40,900
kubera iki?

195
00:12:40,901 --> 00:12:46,008
Kubera ko umutungo wuzuzanya
ushobora kwigana byoroshye igihangano

196
00:12:46,009 --> 00:12:48,730
ndetse n'igicuruzwa ubwacyo.

197
00:12:48,731 --> 00:12:50,798
Reka turebe ku ruhande rwo hepfo rw'ibumoso.

198
00:12:50,799 --> 00:12:54,378
Aha niho horoshye
kwigana ikihangano

199
00:12:54,379 --> 00:12:56,807
kandi mu gihe kimwe,

200
00:12:56,808 --> 00:13:01,830
imitungo yuzuzanya iba
idakenewe cyangwa ibonekera ubuntu.

201
00:13:01,831 --> 00:13:06,807
Muri ubu buryo bwihariye, icyo
wateganya gukora ni ukureba ibyinjiye byinshi.

202
00:13:06,808 --> 00:13:10,998
Abantu bigana igihangano nkuko
bakibona, bazanagicuruza,

203
00:13:10,999 --> 00:13:14,305
kandi hazabaho ibicuruzwa byinshi
mu isoko bisa.

204
00:13:14,306 --> 00:13:18,839
Muri uyu mwihariko, uzizera
kugira intambara ku giciro bivuze

205
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:23,991
ko nta mushinga n'umwe aha
ugiye kunguka cyangwa ufata agaciro.

206
00:13:23,992 --> 00:13:28,567
Kandi, bizaba ko ari abakiriya,
cyangwa abazakoresha igicuruzwa ba nyuma, bazunguka

207
00:13:28,568 --> 00:13:30,763
bagira igiciro kiri hasi
mu isoko.

208
00:13:32,347 --> 00:13:35,526
Kandi hanyuma, reka turebe
ku ruhande rwo hejuru rw'iburyo.

209
00:13:35,527 --> 00:13:37,820
Mu ruhande rwo hejuru rw'iburyo ufite

210
00:13:37,821 --> 00:13:41,182
umutungo wuzuzanya ukomejwe cyane
w'ingenzi,


211
00:13:41,183 --> 00:13:43,667
kandi unafite igicuruzwa

212
00:13:43,668 --> 00:13:46,625
gituruka ku mushoramari
kigoye kwigana.

213
00:13:46,626 --> 00:13:50,847
Icyo kidushyira mu mwanya wo guciririkanya,
ndetse n'umukino wo kumvikana

214
00:13:50,848 --> 00:13:55,185
aho impande zombi ziba zifite imbaraga
kandi nta numwe wasunika amabwiriza.

215
00:13:56,286 --> 00:13:59,458
Kandi muri uyu mwihariko
mushobora kwibaza,

216
00:13:59,459 --> 00:14:02,136
"Ni uruhe ruhande rugiye
gufata agaciro kenshi?"

217
00:14:02,137 --> 00:14:06,405
Kandi biragoye kuvuga aha,
ariko mu kuvugisha ukuri, inshuro nyinshi

218
00:14:06,406 --> 00:14:09,905
kandi ni nyir'umutungo wuzuzanya
ntabwo ari umushoramari

219
00:14:09,906 --> 00:14:11,455
ufata agaciro,

220
00:14:11,456 --> 00:14:14,535
kenshi kubera ko umushoramari
adahagije

221
00:14:14,536 --> 00:14:18,769
kandi ashaka uburenganzira
ku muyoboro cyangwa umutungo

222
00:14:18,770 --> 00:14:20,673
nyir'umutungo wuzuzanya afite

223
00:14:20,674 --> 00:14:23,959
kandi, afite imbaraga
zo guciririkanya nke

224
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:27,741
nubwo nyir'umutungo wuzuzanya
atakigana igicuruzwa cy'umushorabari.

225
00:14:27,742 --> 00:14:32,106
Noneho icyo twavuze
nabihiniye muri iki gishushanyo.

226
00:14:33,202 --> 00:14:39,783
Kandi icyo ushobora kumenya ni:
Niba ntashobora gufata agaciro, naba mpombye?

227
00:14:39,784 --> 00:14:41,486
Naba mfite igitekerezo kibi?

228
00:14:42,751 --> 00:14:45,498
Kandi hari ibisubizo bitandukanye
kuri iki kibazo.

229
00:14:47,001 --> 00:14:49,379
Icyambere ni, mu mabwiriza
yo guha agaciro amahirwe,

230
00:14:49,380 --> 00:14:51,855
mwibutse mu masomo ya mbere:

231
00:14:51,856 --> 00:14:54,638
mu gitekerezo
cyo kumenya amahirwe

232
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:59,136
umushoramari afite amahitamo
yo mu kahe kadirishya

233
00:14:59,137 --> 00:15:01,394
agiye gusorezamo.

234
00:15:02,216 --> 00:15:08,415
Urugera, umushoramari
ashobora guhitamo igicuruzwa cyangwa serivisi

235
00:15:08,416 --> 00:15:10,834
aho igicuruzwa  cyuzuzanya
kiba kiboneka ku buntu.

236
00:15:11,762 --> 00:15:15,268
Cyangwa, cyaba nuko bahanze
ubundi buryo bwo gutanga.

237
00:15:16,088 --> 00:15:19,875
Iyo ukeka urugero rwa mudasobwa za Dell
zahise zigurishwa

238
00:15:19,876 --> 00:15:25,011
kuri telefoni kandi nyuma interineti,
icyo cyari igihangano

239
00:15:25,012 --> 00:15:28,590
mu buryo kirusha
icya guzwe kuri detaye rwose

240
00:15:28,591 --> 00:15:30,434
kiba gisanzwe
mu bubiko bwa buzinesi.

241
00:15:30,435 --> 00:15:33,114
Noneho ntabwo ari ukuvuga, "niba uri
mu bubiko bwa bizinesi,

242
00:15:33,115 --> 00:15:37,870
uhombye kujya ku muntu ucuruza detaye
kandi abadetaye baba bakomey, nibindi."

243
00:15:37,871 --> 00:15:41,065
Ushobora kuzana
uburyo bwawe bw'itanga

244
00:15:41,066 --> 00:15:44,103
buruta
umutungo wuzuzanya waba ushaka.

245
00:15:44,104 --> 00:15:48,814
Noneho icyambere, mu buryo
bwo kugenzura amahirwe

246
00:15:48,815 --> 00:15:52,214
no kumenyekana, gukoresha,

247
00:15:52,215 --> 00:15:56,136
umushoramari ntaba abajijwe rwose

248
00:15:56,137 --> 00:15:58,297
n'ibice bitandukanye hano.

249
00:15:58,298 --> 00:16:01,108
Icyakabiri,
nubwo waba uri mu gice

250
00:16:01,109 --> 00:16:03,199
kitari icy'ingenze cyane,

251
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:06,237
mu yandi magambo ikintu cyose
ariko uruhande rwo hejuru rw'ubumoso hano,

252
00:16:06,238 --> 00:16:07,666
ntabwo urahomba.

253
00:16:07,667 --> 00:16:10,951
nuko uburyo butandukanye bwakoreshejwe
muri zino mwande zitandukanye.

254
00:16:11,589 --> 00:16:14,060
Noneho mu ruhande rw'ubumoso rwo hejuru,
biragaragara.

255
00:16:14,061 --> 00:16:17,912
Biragoye kukwigana, ufite
uburinzi buhagije ku mutungo wawe,

256
00:16:17,913 --> 00:16:20,832
cyangwa birashoboka ko ufite ibigoye
mu bushake bwawe,

257
00:16:20,833 --> 00:16:25,133
kandi rero, ushobora guteganya gusohora
igicuruzwa ku isoko, gufata agaciro,

258
00:16:25,134 --> 00:16:27,173
maze ukagaruza igishoro cyawe

259
00:16:27,174 --> 00:16:30,825
ugafata igihe cyo kuzana
igicuruzwa cyangwa serivise izakurikiraho.

260
00:16:31,397 --> 00:16:36,660
Ariko, mu zindi mpande
ushobora guhatwa

261
00:16:36,667 --> 00:16:42,084
cyangwa byaba byiza kuzana
igisubizo kihuse ku isoko,

262
00:16:42,087 --> 00:16:46,907
cyane cyane ku ruhande rwo hepfo hano
aho byoroshye kwigana.

263
00:16:46,908 --> 00:16:50,669
Biroroshye kwigana igihangano cyawe,
noneho iyo ugeze ku isoko,

264
00:16:50,670 --> 00:16:53,766
uzongera amafaranga bwa mbere,
uzafata agaciro.

265
00:16:53,767 --> 00:16:57,138
Ariko mu gihe kirekire, cyangwa cyo hagati,
ntuzabasha gufata agaciro kenshi

266
00:16:57,139 --> 00:17:00,377
kuko abandi bantu bagiye
kubona, kwigana ndetse no kwinjira.

267
00:17:00,378 --> 00:17:03,228
Noneho ufite gushaka umugambi

268
00:17:03,229 --> 00:17:06,417
gukora inyungu zikomeza
z'igicuruzwa gishya

269
00:17:06,419 --> 00:17:08,637
iyo icyambere kiri ku isoko.

270
00:17:08,637 --> 00:17:09,963
Rero ibi nibyo wita

271
00:17:09,964 --> 00:17:12,963
<i> uburyo bwo kwiyongera </i>
ugereranije  na <i> uburyo buri hamwe</i>.

272
00:17:12,964 --> 00:17:16,313
Uburyo buhagaze ni: usohora
igicuruawa ku isoko,

273
00:17:16,314 --> 00:17:19,029
ufata agaciro
kuko kigoye kukigana.

274
00:17:20,239 --> 00:17:25,227
kandi ushobora
kukibyazamo gucye cyangwa twinshi, nk'uko tuvuga ngo.

275
00:17:25,228 --> 00:17:30,064
Ku rundi ruhande, uburyo bwiyongera
ni aho usohora igicuruzwa ku isoko

276
00:17:30,065 --> 00:17:34,363
kandi ukomeza kucuruza
igicuruzwa gishay mu nyungu zihoraho

277
00:17:34,364 --> 00:17:37,344
bigufasha kubona amafaranga
mu gihe kigufi

278
00:17:37,345 --> 00:17:39,378
mbere yuko wimukira ku kindi.

279
00:17:40,513 --> 00:17:46,280
Noneho ikindi kintu cya nyuma ku masezerano
n'umumaro w'amasezerano.

280
00:17:46,281 --> 00:17:48,760
Kenshi numva abashoramari bavuga,

281
00:17:48,761 --> 00:17:51,461
"Dufite amasezerano kuri bizinesi.
yubakiye ku masezerano.

282
00:17:51,462 --> 00:17:53,406
Amasezerano ni meza."

283
00:17:53,407 --> 00:17:56,701
Ndakeka urebye
kuri iyi ngingo hano,

284
00:17:56,702 --> 00:18:00,970
ushobora kumva impamvu amasezerano
ashobora cyangwa adashobora kuba akomeye?

285
00:18:00,971 --> 00:18:04,602
Iyo amasezerano ari
aya nyir'umutungo wuzuzanya,

286
00:18:05,932 --> 00:18:08,072
Iba ifitwe cyane kandi ni iy'ingenzi,

287
00:18:08,073 --> 00:18:11,972
rero nyir'umutungo wuzuzanya,
mu yandi magambo nyir'amasezerano,

288
00:18:11,973 --> 00:18:17,992
agiye kugica menshi
kugirango ubone uburenganzira kuri uwo mutungo.

289
00:18:19,201 --> 00:18:22,552
Rero, ntabwo
ari garanti

290
00:18:22,553 --> 00:18:26,488
ko kugirana ba nyir'amasezerano benshi

291
00:18:26,489 --> 00:18:29,654
bigiye kukungukira
cyangwa ari igitekerezo cyiza.

292
00:18:30,390 --> 00:18:33,750
Niba nyir'amasezerano agiye
kuyobora amabwiriza,

293
00:18:33,751 --> 00:18:37,448
noneho byarangira bibaye
igitekerezo gihenze.

294
00:18:38,718 --> 00:18:43,258
Noneho mu ncamake y'ibyo twabonye uyu munsi
muri iki gice cyo gufata agaciro:

295
00:18:44,388 --> 00:18:47,817
Twatangiye twiga ku kubonera,

296
00:18:47,818 --> 00:18:50,931
cyangwa ubushobozi bw'umushoramari
mu gufata agaciro.

297
00:18:52,395 --> 00:18:56,214
Nyuma twakoje
twiga ku kwiganana,

298
00:18:56,215 --> 00:19:01,572
cyangwa uko bigoye cyangwa byoroshye kwigana
igihangano cy'umushoramari.

299
00:19:03,533 --> 00:19:06,766
Noneho twavuze ku bicuruzwa byuzuzanya

300
00:19:06,767 --> 00:19:11,205
kandi twabonye n'itandukaniro hagati
y'aho umutungo wuzuzanya

301
00:19:11,206 --> 00:19:16,917
wari uw'ingenzi kdi ufitwe rwose
ugereranije naho uba ari ubuntu cyangwa utari uw'ingenzi.

302
00:19:18,951 --> 00:19:20,278
Nyuma twarebye

303
00:19:20,279 --> 00:19:22,611
kuri izi mbumbane
z'ibigenderwaho

304
00:19:22,612 --> 00:19:27,765
mu kumenya ko hamwe mu hantu heza
ku mushoramari

305
00:19:27,766 --> 00:19:29,841
ari aho biba bigoye kwigana

306
00:19:29,842 --> 00:19:34,481
kandi umutungo wuzuzanya ari
ubuntu cyangwa utari uw'ingenzi.

307
00:19:34,482 --> 00:19:37,849
Kandi birashoboka ko
ahantu hagoye kuba

308
00:19:37,850 --> 00:19:44,018
ari igihe byoroshye kwigana
kandi nyir'umutungo wuzuzanya

309
00:19:44,019 --> 00:19:49,234
ari afitwe ku burenganzira
bwo ku mutungo wuzuzanya w'akamaro.

310
00:19:50,879 --> 00:19:53,297
Kandi hari uburyo bwinshi

311
00:19:53,298 --> 00:19:56,297
bwo kwiga ku bibazo
waba urimo;

312
00:19:56,298 --> 00:19:59,261
uko wakihuta mu gucuruza
kandi ugasohora ibicuruzwa.

313
00:19:59,262 --> 00:20:03,415
Kandi twanavuze
ku gusuzuma amahirwe

314
00:20:03,416 --> 00:20:08,118
no gukoresha umugambi wakugeza
ku gace kamwe cyangwa akandi

315
00:20:08,119 --> 00:20:12,434
ku buryo ushobora kugira
ubucuruzi bwiza

316
00:20:12,435 --> 00:20:14,454
bufata agaciro kenshi.

317
00:20:14,455 --> 00:20:16,483
Murakoze cyane, tuzabonana ikindi gihe.
